title: Multi-vehicle crash on the Mass Pike causing delays - Massachusetts news
text:
A multi-vehicle crash has traffic reduced to a single lane on the Massachusetts Turnpike in Westborough, according to state police .
The accident happened this morning on the Pike westbound.
